  ],
  "remarks": "Iran Liquefied Natural Gas Co. is managing Iran LNG projects. It is a subsidiary of the National Iranian Gas Export Company, which is itself a subsidiary of the State-owned National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC). The National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC) is a State-owned and operated entity providing substantial financial resources and support to the Government of Iran. The main shareholder of Iran Liquefied Natural Gas Co is the Government of Iran. Therefore, Iran Liquefied Natural Gas Co. is owned and controlled by an entity providing support to the Government of Iran.",
